    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @JonnyTurnerUK,\n\nYou want to use instantsearch.js in a context where the user has to submit a form and be redirected to another webpage?\n\nI am unsure why would you need instantsearch.js for then, since it was built for instant page updates? Maybe I am missing some context here.\n\nThe best way would be for you to give us access to some live environement demonstrating the issue.\n\nThanks\n",
